application. The extraction commit records the exact source revision in its
message ("Initial extraction from knottyyoga@<SHA>").

This product bundles no third-party source, but links the following libraries at
build time, each under its own license (obtained via Conan): Boost, Crow,
libpqxx, OpenSSL, libsodium, mailio, GoogleTest, Abseil, HowardHinnant/date,
libcurl, libjpeg, libpng, libtiff, and zlib.
